      "message": "This part of configuration is commented using the \"!\" char to distinguish between an original comment starting with \"#\" and a commented config line.\n\nI preferred to keep log4j 1.x configurations in case we needed to revert back to log4j 1.x.\n\nAll the configs before \"#########log4j2 Configuration############\" are commented out.",
